data.description: Discover this fully renovated brick ranch in Hallwood! This 1,463 sq. ft. home boasts 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a sleek kitchen with shaker cabinets and granite countertops. The primary bathroom is brand new. Enjoy a unique room off the primary bedroom, perfect for a walk-in closet or home office with a cozy fireplace. Located in a quiet neighborhood just a few miles from the beach, plus easy access to Langley, I-64, and shopping. Don't miss this Hallwood gem – schedule a viewing today!
